data.description: This detached condo is a newly updated Urban Oasis with new flooring, new fixtures, new sinks, new paint, new quartz countertops throughout, new insulation and a newer water heater. Sittings at the end of a small private road with only 9 other homes that make up the small homeowner run HOA.A quiet area yet conveniently close to I-205 & 99E, city parks, schools, river access, shopping and restaurants. Covered patio and front landscaping with sprinklers, gas hookup in back of house for a grill, small dog park across the lane. Oversized single car garage with cadet heater. Monthly HOA dues include water, sewer & landscaping. Owner Occupy Only! Oregon City Schools.
